# Implementation Plan: Features & UI Polish

The user wants to add Voice Entries, Mood Analytics, Heatmap Calendar, Smart Reminders, and an AI Summary, while upgrading the UI to a "Glassmorphism" style.

## Dependencies
- `flutter_heatmap_calendar`: For the contribution graph.
- [record](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#139-161): For audio recording.
- `audioplayers`: For playback.
- `permission_handler`: For microphone permissions.
- `path_provider`: For file storage.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Configuration & Setup
- **[pubspec.yaml](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/pubspec.yaml)**: Add new packages.
- **[ios/Runner/Info.plist](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/ios/Runner/Info.plist)**: Add `NSMicrophoneUsageDescription`.

### 2. UI Components (Glassmorphism)
- **`lib/widgets/glass_container.dart`**: New widget wrapping `BackdropFilter` and `Container` with semi-transparent white/black colors and blur.
- **[lib/theme/app_colors.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/theme/app_colors.dart)**: Add glass-specific colors.

### 3. Data Model
- **[lib/models/journal_entry.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/models/journal_entry.dart)**: Add `String? audioPath` field.
- **[lib/services/store.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/services/store.dart)**: Handle audio file persistence.

### 4. Features

#### A. Voice Entries
- **`lib/widgets/audio_recorder.dart`**: Button to hold-and-record.
- **`lib/widgets/audio_player.dart`**: Simple play/pause bubble.
- **[lib/screens/today_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart)**: Integrate recorder/player in the actions page.

#### B. Analytics (Mood & Heatmap)
- **`lib/screens/analytics_screen.dart`**: New screen.
- **Mood Chart**: Re-use logic from `StatsScreen` but polish with `fl_chart`.
- **Heatmap**: Use `HeatMapCalendar` to show activity intensity.
- **AI Summary**: Simple word frequency analysis of recent entries to display "Week in 3 Words".

#### C. Smart Reminders
- **[lib/services/notification_service.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/services/notification_service.dart)**: Add `scheduleInactivityReminder()`.
- **Logic**: Check `lastJournalDate` on app open; if > 2 days, schedule a notification for tomorrow.

### 5. Integration
- **[lib/screens/main_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/main_screen.dart)**: Update navigation to include Analytics. Apply Glassmorphism.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Build test to ensure new dependencies don't break the build.
- `flutter test` not applicable for UI/Audio without mocks, but we will ensure compilation.

### Manual Verification
- **Voice**: Record a clip, save, restart app, verify playback.
- **Analytics**: Verify chart renders and heatmap reflects entries.
- **UI**: Visually inspect the "Glass" effect on the Simulator.
